OL,3,CAnger over planned closures of care
OL,4,Chomes and day centres in Derbyshire
OL,6,FDerbyshire council's cabinet has
OL,7,Fagreed to introduce a raft of cutbacks
OL,8,Fand money-saving changes in four key
OL,9,Fareas involving care home closures,
OL,10,Fcuts to learning disability services,
OL,11,Fcommunity group funding, and tighter
OL,12,Fcriteria for home support eligibility.
OL,14,FThe Conservative-led council agreed at
OL,15,Fa cabinet meeting today (Thursday,
OL,16,FNovember 14), to approve the redesign
OL,17,Fof elderly care services with the
OL,18,Fclosure of eight care homes and five
OL,19,Fday centres for the elderly under
OL,20,Frefreshed proposals after studying the
OL,21,Fpublic reaction.
