OL,3,CAnger over planned closures of care
OL,4,Chomes and day centres in Derbyshire
OL,6,FFollowing further consultations, the
OL,7,Fcabinet also approved discontinuing
OL,8,Ffour Day Opportunity Centres and four
OL,9,FShort Break Residential Units for
OL,10,Fadults with learning disabilities and
OL,11,For autism, and to withdraw
OL,12,FDiscretionary Grant Funding for 50
OL,13,Fvoluntary and community groups, and to
OL,14,Fintroduce tighter eligibility criteria
OL,15,Ffor its Derbyshire Healthy Homes
OL,16,FProject service.
OL,18,FOriginal plans
