OL,6,FIn original plans the council had
OL,7,Fearmarked 11 care homes for possible
OL,8,Fclosure including: Briar Close,
OL,9,FBorrowash; Bennerley Fields, Ilkeston;
OL,10,FCastle Court, Swadlincote; Florence
OL,11,FShipley, Heanor; The Grange,
OL,12,FEckington; Lacemaker Court, Long
OL,13,FEaton; The Leys, Ashbourne; New
OL,14,FBassett House, Shirebrook; Rowthorne,
OL,15,FSwanwick; Thomas Colledge House,
OL,16,FBolsover; And Whitestones, at Chapel-
OL,17,Fen-le-Frith.
