OL,3,CAnger over planned closures of care
OL,4,Chomes and day centres in Derbyshire
OL,6,FBut the council has now agreed to
OL,7,Fcease to operate and offer for sale
OL,8,Feight care homes including: Briar
OL,9,FClose, Castle Court, The Grange,
OL,10,FLacemaker Court, The Leys, New Bassett
OL,11,FHouse, Rowthorne, Thomas Colledge.
OL,13,FAnd Bennerley will no longer operate
OL,14,Fas a residential care home and will be
OL,15,Frepurposed to be used exclusively for
OL,16,Fcommunity support beds for short-term
OL,17,F'reablement' and assessment.
OL,19,FFurther public consultations
