OL,4,Chomes and day centres in Derbyshire
OL,6,FThe council has also stated it is
OL,7,Fproposing further public consultations
OL,8,Fon proposed changes to its remaining
OL,9,Fresidential care homes in a move
OL,10,Ftowards 'a single operating model of
OL,11,Fcare' with four homes operating as
OL,12,Fspecialist dementia care homes
OL,13,Fincluding Florence Shipley,
OL,14,FWhitestones, Matlock's Meadow View,
OL,15,Fand Swadlincotes' Oaklands, with all
OL,16,Fexcept Whitestones having an
OL,17,Fintegrated day centre.
