OL,4,Chomes and day centres in Derbyshire
OL,6,FAnother option under consideration is
OL,7,Ffor two homes to operate as specialist
OL,8,Fdementia care homes including Florence
OL,9,FShipley and Whitestones with Meadow
OL,10,FView and Oaklands adopting a mixed
OL,11,Fcare model.
OL,13,FThe council has also agreed to close
OL,14,Ffive day centres for the elderly
OL,15,Fincluding Blackwell Day Centre,
OL,16,FBlackwell; Fabrick Day Services,
OL,17,FHilton; Jubilee Centre, New Mills;
OL,18,FQueens Court, Buxton; And Valley View
OL,19,FDay Centre, Bolsover.
