OL,6,FIt has also agreed that three day
OL,7,Fcentres originally considered for
OL,8,Fclosure will remain open including:
OL,9,FEccles Fold, at Chapel en-le-Frith;
OL,10,FHasland Resource Centre, in
OL,11,FChesterfield; and Shirevale, in
OL,12,FShirebrook.
