OL,4,Chomes and day centres in Derbyshire
OL,6,FThe council claims the changes support
OL,7,Fthe council's intention to create a
OL,8,Fsustainable service focusing on
OL,9,Fspecialist services for people with
OL,10,Fdementia and their carers, offering
OL,11,Flong-term residential care and
OL,12,Fflexible day and overnight breaks to
OL,13,Fsupport carers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
