OL,3,CAnger over planned closures of care
OL,4,Chomes and day centres in Derbyshire
OL,6,FIt also claims the changes will allow
OL,7,Ffor greater integration with health
OL,8,Fpartners to provide short-term support
OL,9,Fand assessment services to help timely
OL,10,Fdischarges from hospital, prevent
OL,11,Funplanned hospital admissions and
OL,12,Freduce the risk of readmission helping
OL,13,Fpeople stay at home.
OL,15,FUNISON campaigners had called for the
OL,16,Fcouncil to abandon adult social care
OL,17,Fsaving plans and Derbyshire Labour MPs
OL,18,Falso met with council leader, Cllr
OL,19,FBarry Lewis, to express their concerns
OL,20,Fand opposition to the plans to close
OL,21,Fcare homes and elderly day centres.
