OL,3,CAnger over planned closures of care
OL,4,Chomes and day centres in Derbyshire
OL,6,FDuring considerations, the council
OL,7,Falso rejected a call from opposition
OL,8,FLabour Group councillors, including
OL,9,FLabour Group Leader Cllr Joan Dixon,
OL,10,Fto further investigate subsequent long-
OL,11,Fterm care costs before deciding on the
OL,12,Fproposed closures.
OL,14,FCllr Dixon has said the impact of the
OL,15,Fcuts will be 'devastating' and she
OL,16,Fclaims the Conservative-led council's
OL,17,Ffinancial management is to blame for
OL,18,Fthe situation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
