OL,3,CAnger over planned closures of care
OL,4,Chomes and day centres in Derbyshire
OL,6,FHowever, the council which is
OL,7,Faddressing saving proposals to manage
OL,8,Fa budget deficit of over #39m for the
OL,9,F2024/25 financial year is blaming
OL,10,Freduced Government funding, the impact
OL,11,Ffrom the Covid-19 pandemic, inflation
OL,12,Frates, higher prices for fuel, energy
OL,13,Fand materials, rising costs, meeting
OL,14,Fthe cost of the national pay award and
OL,15,Fthe growing demand for adults' and
OL,16,Fchildren's social care services.
